  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, you store extra Water in your body, giving you an amount of uses equal to your proficiency bonus per long rest. </p><p>You can use these reservoirs to empower a ninjutsu with the Water Release Keyword, either increases its damage by 1 damage die or save DC by +1. </p><p>At 11th level, increase the damage die or save DC by 2 and at 18th level, increase the damage die or save DC by 3.</p>",
